The '''Kenu Clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on the planet [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. A major rival of the [[Bomu Clan]]—considered by them rank amateurs—it pledged support to the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] in the final years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]].

